title: $:/plugins/rimir/llm-connect/examples/summarize-to-field
tags: $:/tags/rimir/llm-connect/example
example-name: Summarize to field
example-description: Summarize a tiddler and store the result in its llm-summary field
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

!! Summarize to field

Uses a prompt template that references the default context template and sets `output-target: field:llm-summary`. The summary is persisted on the tiddler.

''Settings covered:'' action mode, `output-mode: text`, `output-target: field:llm-summary`, precedence via prompt template

```
<$button>
  Summarize to field
  <$llm-action
    tiddler=<<currentTiddler>>
    promptTemplate="$:/plugins/rimir/llm-connect/prompts/summarize"
  />
</$button>
```

!!! Live demo

<$button>
